scene.message:
Male Student: Oh, you came{nl}
too, {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{clearbox}Look at this! With these, we{nl}
can stand up to demons{nl}
whenever they come!!{waitkey}{ret}

Male Student: Huh? The stock{nl}
here's different from last{nl}
time. Even more dangerous{nl}
somehow...{waitkey}{ret}

Teacher: Who is that child?!{waitkey}This is a school!! Don't go{nl}
opening a shop without{nl}
permission!!{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: Welcome~ Me come{nl}
from Demon Mountain. Me bring{nl}
very good things~{waitkey}{clearbox}Mister, you need this. Me{nl}
give good price. You buy,{nl}
yes!{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: Been waiting!{nl}
Mister, you lucky~{waitkey}{clearbox}Shop close very soon. Last{nl}
sale — you no buy, you lose!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Came from Demon{nl}
Mountain? Then is that kid{nl}
a demon too?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Making humans and{nl}
demons fight for profit. What{nl}
an outrageous kid, honestly!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: How many times has{nl}
that kid saved our lives.{waitkey}{clearbox}Even if we're overcharged a{nl}
bit, we ought to be grateful.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Dehya~ What's with this{nl}
kid, selling dangerous stuff{nl}
at school?{waitkey}{clearbox}Ah well, no use sweating the{nl}
small stuff.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: That kid is apparently{nl}
a merchant of death from the{nl}
Demon world.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Whether we or the Queen{nl}
wins, I suppose it makes no{nl}
difference to that child?{waitkey}{ret}
